  ${
    $d k j n $.
    $( The sum of the reciprocals of the triangle numbers converge to two.
       (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 23-Apr-2014.)  (Revised by Mario Carneiro,
       22-May-2014.) $)
    trirecip $p |- sum_ k e. NN ( 2 / ( k x. ( k + 1 ) ) ) = 2 $=
      ( vn cn c2 cv c1 caddc co cmul cdiv csu wcel cc wceq 2cn a1i syl wtru cli
